Pre-Game Insights: The match is the first T20I of Australia's tour of Scotland 2024.
Scotland is hosting the series and aims to perform well on home soil.
Australia is known for their aggressive and disciplined approach.
Travis Head is the captain of Australia and Mitchell Marsh is a key batter.
George Munsey is the wicketkeeper for Scotland and Richie Berrington is a crucial batter.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match will be live streamed on Fancode.
The venue is Grange Cricket Club in Edinburgh.
